  "id": "api/common/formatCurrency",
  "title": "formatCurrency",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/i18n/format_number.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L124-L158\" aria-label=\"建议修改\" title=\"建议修改\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/common/src/i18n/format_number.ts#L124-L158\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common/formatCurrency\", \"name\": \"formatCurrency\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"formatcurrency\">formatCurrency<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/formatCurrency#formatcurrency\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">稳定</label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Formats a number as currency using locale rules.</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <a href=\"api/common/formatCurrency\" class=\"code-anchor\">formatCurrency</a>(value: number, <a href=\"api/common/NgLocaleLocalization#locale\" class=\"code-anchor\">locale</a>: string, currency: string, currencyCode?: string, digitsInfo?: string): string</code-example>\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"参数\">参数</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>value</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code>number</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>locale</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code>string</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>currency</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code>string</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>currencyCode</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code>string</code>.</p>\n      <p translation-result=\"\">可选. 默认值是 <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>digitsInfo</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code>string</code>.</p>\n      <p translation-result=\"\">可选. 默认值是 <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值\">返回值</h4>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>string</code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/formatCurrency#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-origin=\"off\">Use <code>currency</code> to format a number as currency.</p>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">Where:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>value</code> is a number.</li>\n<li><code><a href=\"api/common/NgLocaleLocalization#locale\" class=\"code-anchor\">locale</a></code> is a <code>string</code> defining the locale to use.</li>\n<li><code>currency</code> is the string that represents the currency, it can be its symbol or its name.</li>\n<li><code>currencyCode</code> is the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217\">ISO 4217</a> currency code, such\nas <code>USD</code> for the US dollar and <code>EUR</code> for the euro.</li>\n<li><code>digitInfo</code> See <a href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe\"><code>DecimalPipe</code></a> for more details.</li>\n</ul>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/DecimalPipe\n - api/common/NgLocaleLocalization#locale\n - api/common/formatCurrency#description\n - api/common/formatCurrency#formatcurrency\n - https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/i18n/format_number.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L124-L158\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/common/src/i18n/format_number.ts#L124-L158\n-->"
